title: r/Maliciouscompliance How I Traumatized My Teacher!
description:
r/Maliciouscompliance The teacher in today's video thinks that students shouldn't be allowed to use lip balm, for some reason. Lady, what on earth is wrong with lip balm? After the teacher confiscates a young girl's lip balm, the student decides to get malicious compliance by traumatizing the teacher with a horrifying bloody smile that drips all over desk! If you like this video and want to see more, hit that subscribe button!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EftC2_cBkqY
